Class FeatureLuminosity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.st.BlueSTSDK.Feature
      • com.st.BlueSTSDK.Features.FeatureLuminosity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FeatureRandomLuminosity

    public class FeatureLuminosity
extends Feature
    Feature that contains the data comes form a luminosity sensor.

    Node: since the sensor is the same, it is possible that you can not have data from a proximity sensor and from a luminosity sensor at the same time

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    STMicroelectronics - Central Labs.
